{"tid":1972103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[遊戲情報] 真。牆國！中國要禁全球同服、單機實名制！","createTime":"2020-04-14T10:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T13:53:25.000Z","uid":28114,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b95b7f23bf1ea3299e9018328fb8cf1fa39987","tid":1972103,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabf6vx.png?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaabf6vx.png%3F_w%3D750&h=f5eedd10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾天強國才傳出要BAN掉《動物森友會》的消息，現在又有進一步消息指出，要實施史上最嚴厲的遊戲規範，真的要在牆內圈圈玩遊戲惹~<br />\n<br />\n據遊戲葡萄報導，遊戲的新禁令不僅限於廣東，連上海、北京都同步跟進，內文實在是落落長，節錄以下規範重點列述，有興趣的可以自己去研究原文：<br />\n<br />\n1. 遊戲出版禁止換皮在多地申報，違者暫停遊戲出版業務6個月（禁換皮遊戲耶，這算德政吧？<br />\n2. 主機遊戲與小遊戲要求營運平台要完成實名認證<br />\n3. 連線遊戲（端對端，非連線到伺服器）與純單機在下載與購買時要完成實名認證<br />\n4. 所有既有未認證用戶，也要完成實名認證，若無認證受到投訴，也要按照最新的實名認證和防沉迷要求進行處罰（任天堂不審核言論是吧，直接從源頭控管，買遊戲也要實名認證上線啦！）<br />\n5. 不得在遊戲宣揚「全球共同伺服器」功能，如果有，應該即時下架及刪除該功能<br />\n6. 不得在遊戲中出現殭屍、瘟疫等對應武漢肺炎疫情的題材，確保遊戲聊天命名系統不會出現不當言論等等&hellip;<br />\n7. 譴責部分玩家利用地圖創造玩法、地圖編輯功能，自行編輯遊戲世界，宣揚分裂祖國思想"},{"pid":"3ef2c02b1a014a9c251729473b32d0158561c5a9","tid":1972103,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"越想越覺得是受之前ｍｅｍｅ圖影響...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabf6EU.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaabf6EU.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=32849e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabf6ET.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaabf6ET.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=8b7f4565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabf6EV.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaabf6EV.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=23f9f4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaabf6vZ.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaabf6vZ.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=bedcac01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫QQ 這下子還要玩啥XDD 下次遇到小粉紅要先問候一聲，「你實名制了嗎？」<br />\n這文案一出，連牆內都在講，史上最嚴的遊戲審查制度降臨惹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-5187071-1-1.html?fbclid=IwAR0D7eLAo1DIn8-4_kxf3mRJIg1GRebmryxbKqGgPxZnlzTG52KbTU26uvM&amp;utm_campaign=20200413&amp;utm_medium=ck101_ED&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-5187071-1-1.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0D7eLAo1DIn8-4_kxf3mRJIg1GRebmryxbKqGgPxZnlzTG52KbTU26uvM%26utm_campaign%3D20200413%26utm_medium%3Dck101_ED%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=11c1a47c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-5187071-1-1.html?fbclid=IwAR0D7eLAo1DIn8-4_kxf3mRJIg1GRebmryxbKqGgPxZnlzTG52KbTU26uvM&amp;utm_campaign=20200413&amp;utm_medium=ck101_ED&amp;utm_source=facebook</a>"},{"pid":"365e3d87a1f6321925e56e7076ebed1e6ce9092b","tid":1972103,"uid":231522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"終於唔洗見到大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋仲有VPN 屌"},{"pid":"9a7a8edb485266a7199af34e64253f6588a6c2d1","tid":1972103,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3a7413dd8dd2d278235b30e421daf130864b4e","tid":1972103,"uid":269629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"之前仲有人講變左打機抗爭...<br />\n結果原來好撚有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49988cb9d46c505faa7d5d8aaff2b00ad3fdcfa9","tid":1972103,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"以為每個game開個ser俾中國自己搵算啦<br />\n唔好搞到外面"},{"pid":"38d83b26f919e0d3